ED_Title: Financing of the United  Nations Mission in East Timor
ED_DecisionText: At its 108th plenary meeting, on 6 September 2024, the General Assembly decided to include the item entitled “Financing of the United Nations Mission in East Timor” in the draft agenda of its seventy-ninth session.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the resumed part of the session will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
